  <summary date="2024-04-04T15:31:21Z" status="Introduced in House">Study on Improving Lands Act

This bill requires the Department of Agriculture to (1) direct a study on the state of soil health on federal lands that determines impacts such as grazing, wildfire, recreation, and invasive species; and (2) create a database of the information collected during the study.</summary>
